{"tid":2317532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對面武漢看過來","createTime":"2020-12-08T15:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T16:10:36.000Z","uid":195136,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1254f1f46c9f11dd8352e9c2b38972b92e6723a9","tid":2317532,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"對面的武漢看過來 <br />\n看過來 看過來 <br />\n香港的表演很精彩 <br />\n請不要假裝不理不睬 <br />\n對面的武漢看過來 <br />\n看過來 看過來 <br />\n不要被我的肺炎嚇壞 <br />\n其實我很可愛  <br />\n笨柒林鄭的悲哀 <br />\n說出來 誰明白 <br />\n求求你拋個媚眼過來 <br />\n哄哄我 逗我樂開懷  ( 呵呵 沒人理我 ) <br />\n我左看右看 上看下看 <br />\n原來每個高官都不簡單 <br />\n我想了又想 我猜了又猜 <br />\n高官們的心事還真奇怪  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023eb19d4f1d7cd0c6eec68b63d4e0f7a1d74016","tid":2317532,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25c11afa79243331c06b93dc3b45f1ce3c4b048","tid":2317532,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f425893be30729d3346f6e71141e41276cdf7304","tid":2317532,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"又無得出街食飯<br />\n好餓"},{"pid":"f7ccc4d8b0983b268160f04b168df957ff831190","tid":2317532,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1e52258f2a76a9760b8572d2c2c148be63e664","tid":2317532,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7ccc4d8b0983b268160f04b168df957ff831190","tid":2317532,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:53:51.000